<div id="post-564" class="post-564 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-gry">

<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://ynleborg.pl/?p=564" title="Permalink to The feeling of fulfilment" rel="bookmark">The feeling of fulfilment</a></h2>

<div class="entry-meta">
<span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2015-09-02T17:19:03+0000">2 wrzesnia 2015</abbr></span>					<span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://ynleborg.pl/?author=1" title="View all posts by Jacek Grobelny">Jacek Grobelny</a></span>				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->


<div class="entry-content">
<p>After nearly thirty hours of absolute joy:<br />
<a href="http://ynleborg.pl/priv/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/203160_screenshots_2015-09-01_00001.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-565 size-large" src="http://ynleborg.pl/priv/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/203160_screenshots_2015-09-01_00001-1024x576.jpg" alt="203160_screenshots_2015-09-01_00001" width="640" height="360" srcset="http://ynleborg.pl/priv/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/203160_screenshots_2015-09-01_00001-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://ynleborg.pl/priv/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/203160_screenshots_2015-09-01_00001-300x169.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>I&#8217;m a fan of  the series since I&#8217;ve laid my hand on the psx controller back in 1997. I was loyal, even that every next game was worse. But this 2013 reboot was a blast for me! I can not wait for Rise of the Tomb Raider!</p>
